My first movie I got to join in the directing world is out! I was blessed to call this my first TAD (Trainee Assistant Director) gig for a couple days! @lucieguest thank you for welcoming me with open arms and being so patient and kind with me. To all the cast and crew, thank you for being so kind and making the days full of laughs and success. You too @thedarienmartin cause you’re bigger than me 🤝🏾💪🏾😂 Miss you ALL! Go check it out on @eentertainment ! 🎬☺️
Thank you @whitecapsfc for welcoming and showing me your home ⚽️🫶🏾
